<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   President Bush's ``honeymoon'' with Congress
ended a long time ago, his spokesman suggested Thursday.
   Presidential press secretary Marlin Fitzwater said Bush still
hopes to reach bipartisan agreements with the Democratic-controlled
